Products covered by this EPD satisfy general purpose concrete as used in residential, commercial, and public works applications in the United States. This EPD reports the impacts for 30 different ready0mixed concrete products produce at 9 different CalPortland facilities in accordance  with the following:
ACI 211: Standard Practice for Selecting Proportions for Norman, Heavyweight, and Mass Concerte
ACI 318: Building Code Requirements for Structural Concerete
ASTM C94: Standard Specification for Ready-Mixed Concrete
UNSOC Code 30111500: Ready Mix
